description:
No special hardware is required for this app. Simply ask any of the following to hear a cool fact about Maryland!
"Alexa, ask Maryland facts to ": 
a fact
a Maryland fact
tell me a fact
tell me a Maryland fact
give me a fact
give me a Maryland fact
tell me trivia
tell me a Maryland trivia
give me trivia
give me a Maryland trivia
give me some information
give me some Maryland information
tell me something
give me something
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Maryland Facts to tell me a Maryland fact.
name: Maryland Facts!
shortDescription: Maryland Facts! is a trivia app that tells you interesting facts about Maryland. Use it to learn cool facts to impress your friends.
